'''Mount Neustruyev''' (also known as '''Gora Neustruyeva''') is a peak in [[East Antarctica]], 2,900 m, standing 5&nbsp;mi NNE of [[Gneiskopf Peak]] in [[SÃ¼dliche Petermann Range]], [[Wohlthat Mountains]], [[Queen Maud Land]].
